changeSet.createView: SELECT taskinstan0_.token_ AS id_situacao_processo, pooledacto2_.actorid_ AS nm_pooled_actor, fluxo.id_fluxo, processdef6_.name_ AS nm_fluxo, task4_.name_ AS nm_tarefa, tj.id_tarefa, c.id_caixa, c.nm_caixa, proce.id_processo, taskinstan0_.procinst_ AS id_process_instance, taskinstan0_.id_ AS id_task_instance, taskinstan0_.task_ AS id_task, taskinstan0_.actorid_ AS nm_actorid FROM jbpm_taskinstance taskinstan0_ LEFT JOIN tb_tarefa_jbpm tj ON tj.id_jbpm_task = taskinstan0_.task_ LEFT JOIN tb_tarefa tbtarefa ON tbtarefa.id_tarefa = tj.id_tarefa LEFT JOIN tb_fluxo fluxo ON fluxo.id_fluxo = tbtarefa.id_fluxo LEFT JOIN jbpm_taskactorpool pooledacto1_ ON taskinstan0_.id_ = pooledacto1_.taskinstance_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_pooledactor pooledacto2_ ON pooledacto1_.pooledactor_ = pooledacto2_.id_ RIGHT JOIN tb_processo proce ON proce.id_processo = (( SELECT DISTINCT ( SELECT DISTINCT longinstan1_.longvalue_ FROM jbpm_variableinstance longinstan1_ WHERE longinstan1_.class_ = 'L' AND longinstan1_.name_ = 'processo' AND longinstan1_.processinstance_ = longinstan3_.processinstance_) AS longvalue_ FROM jbpm_variableinstance longinstan3_ WHERE longinstan3_.token_ = taskinstan0_.token_)) LEFT JOIN tb_caixa c ON proce.id_caixa = c.id_caixa LEFT JOIN jbpm_task task4_ ON taskinstan0_.task_ = task4_.id_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_processinstance processins5_ ON taskinstan0_.procinst_ = processins5_.id_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_processdefinition processdef6_ ON processins5_.processdefinition_ = processdef6_.id_ WHERE (EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM jbpm_taskinstance taskinstan7_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_taskactorpool pooledacto8_ ON taskinstan7_.id_ = pooledacto8_.taskinstance_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_pooledactor pooledacto9_ ON pooledacto8_.pooledactor_ = pooledacto9_.id_, jbpm_task task10_ WHERE taskinstan7_.task_ = task10_.id_ AND taskinstan7_.issuspended_ = 0 AND taskinstan7_.isopen_ = 1 AND taskinstan0_.id_ = taskinstan7_.id_));

changeSet.author: liquibase
changeSet.createView: SELECT ncf.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, f.qt_prazo, (SELECT avg(pt.nr_tempo_gasto) AS avg FROM (SELECT pe.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, p.dt_fim, pe.nr_tempo_gasto FROM tb_processo p JOIN tb_processo_epa pe ON p.id_processo = pe.id_processo JOIN tb_natureza_categoria_fluxo n ON n.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo = pe.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo) pt WHERE ((NOT (pt.dt_fim IS NULL)) AND (pt.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo = ncf.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo)) GROUP BY pt.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo) AS nr_tempo_medio FROM (tb_natureza_categoria_fluxo ncf JOIN tb_fluxo f ON ncf.id_fluxo = f.id_fluxo);

changeSet.author: liquibase
changeSet.createView: SELECT tempostarefas.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, tb_tarefa.id_tarefa, tb_tarefa.ds_tarefa, tb_tarefa.nr_prazo, tb_tarefa.tp_prazo, tempostarefas.nr_tempo_medio FROM (tb_tarefa JOIN ( SELECT p.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, pet.id_tarefa, avg(pet.nr_tempo_gasto) AS nr_tempo_medio FROM (tb_processo_epa_tarefa pet JOIN tb_processo_epa p ON p.id_processo = pet.id_processo) WHERE ((NOT (pet.dt_fim IS NULL)) AND (pet.nr_tempo_gasto > 0)) GROUP BY pet.id_tarefa, p.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo) tempostarefas ON tb_tarefa.id_tarefa = tempostarefas.id_tarefa);

changeSet.sql: CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [tb_prioridade_processo_ak] ON [dbo].[tb_prioridade_processo] ( [nr_peso] ASC , [ds_prioridade_processo] ASC ) WHERE ( [nr_peso] IS NOT NULL AND [ds_prioridade_processo] IS NOT NULL ) WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, SORT_IN_TEMPDB = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, DROP_EXISTING = OFF, ONLINE = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY];
